features: 【Extra Large Storage Capacity Desk】: 3 fabric drawers under the main desktop are convenient for everything you need for both work and study, giving you plenty of storage space. Another desktop with one drawer and one file cabinet underneath allows you to conveniently place and organize a variety of items. With this large storage computer desk, you can keep your desk tidy, whether it's for documents, office or school supplies, gaming equipment, and more.

【2 USB Charging Ports & 3 Power Outlets】: This home office desk is equipped with 3 power outlets and 2 USB charging ports to quickly charge smartphones, Bluetooth, headphones, tablets, mobile power, and gaming devices. You can work enjoyably or play games easily with a full charge!

【Reversible L Desk with Two-tier Shelves】: This gaming desk has two storage shelves helping you accommodate more books and documents needed for office and study while strengthening the desk's weight-bearing capacity. The left and right interchangeable design allows this l-shaped desk to be placed in any corner of your room or office area, providing you with great convenience.

【Sturdy & Uniquely Designed Desk】: This writing desk is made of high-quality particle board and durable metal frames. Adjustable feet not only protect the floor from scratches but also ensure stability on uneven surfaces. The X-bars design allows you to stretch your legs while working, keeping you sitting comfortably. The workstation desk with a host stand and versatile storage space perfectly meet your needs. Ideal desk for bedroom, office, and study room use, helping you free up space.

【Easy Assembly & After-sale Service】: Our product package contains labeled parts, detailed instructions, and all assembly tools. You just need to follow the instructions step by step. AODK provides customer service before and after purchase. If you have any problems with the product you received please feel free to contact us, we will provide you with a satisfactory solution within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for price
reviews.reviewText: This was great for the price. Easy to install! There was one piece that we didn't understand where to put it, but it seems to be a part of a printer tray. Didn't impact the integrity or look of the desk though.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent for the price
reviews.reviewText: After having to return the item that was not a desk, i went through Amazon customer service and ordered a replacement for free with free shipping. The desk arrived a day early and I spent several hours putting it together because i did 99% of the work myself. Instructions are pretty clear if you're paying attention - which i was not. The composite wood is very nice, flexible when trying to put the desk together and the metal framing is very solid. I am happy to finally have an l-desk back and having the room i was hoping for. I got the larger desk as i knew i had just enough room to fit it in my corner of the master bedroom. The platform where the PC sits on is really nice, makes it much easier to move my PC around when rearranging and i am happy it has plastic sliders that screw into it.After all of the painstaking time of waiting for the correct item to arrive - i am overall pleased with the amount of storage, the sturdiness and overall look of this l-desk, and recommend it to people due to it's extremely affordable price. Who knows, i might make my company buy me the shorter one for when i move offices at this price and ease of putting together if you have more than one person doing it.Good job. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for the money!
reviews.reviewText: I love my desk! It was a great investment! I have to say the manufacturer’s assembly instructions are the best I've seen! They recommend two people to assemble due to the layout and amount of pieces and parts. I am not a handy person, so taking this project on solo was ambitious but DOABLE because of the instructions! The desk is roomy and for the most part, fits together perfectly! I love the fabric drawers—and the amount of space they offer. The color was spot-on gray. And the power cord is wonderful! Shipping was on time too.I recommend this purchase for the aesthetic and quality, functionality, and price! Best of all I didn't have to wait for my husband to put it together. 👏 Also, there's a QR code for the desk assembly!
